<div id="tf-services" class="text-center">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="section-title center">
            <h2>Take a look at <strong>our service sites</strong></h2>
            <div class="line">
                <hr>
            </div>
            <div class="clearfix"></div>
            <small><em>The Crimson Circle is one of the few service organizations that does not have a service focus. This allows us to explore and appreciate many different types of service, while also being flexible to account for the many interests of our members. Here are four of our weekly service sites.</em></small>
        </div>
